show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description: Once a powerful CEO, Ananya Sharma vanishes from the corporate world only to reappear as a janitor in her own company. But when the firm is on the brink of collapse and Aryan Mehta, a rising star, seeks guidance, he discovers her hidden identity. What follows is a gripping tale of redemption, resilience, and a woman reclaiming the legacy she never lost. Watch Now!
